WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:11.789 --> 00:00:14.250
Finally. it is mine.

2
00:00:16.628 --> 00:00:18.588
Not if I have anything
to say about it.

3
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

4
00:00:47.701 --> 00:00:49.328
You think you can stop me?

5
00:00:49.495 --> 00:00:50.704
I know I can.

6
00:01:10.265 --> 00:01:11.642
It is only fair to warn you

7
00:01:11.809 --> 00:01:13.644
that I have trained
with the best.

8
00:01:13.811 --> 00:01:16.897
It's only fair to warn you.
so have I.

9
00:01:18.732 --> 00:01:21.318
You are very confident.
too confident.

10
00:01:21.694 --> 00:01:23.570
Since we are both
honorable fighters.

11
00:01:23.737 --> 00:01:25.239
I shall offer you a deal.

12
00:01:25.406 --> 00:01:29.493
If I cannot defeat you
in three moves. I shall surrender.

13
00:01:29.827 --> 00:01:32.454
You can have 50 moves.
and I'll still defeat you.

14
00:01:38.335 --> 00:01:40.254
I'm afraid you'll have to do
better than that.

15
00:01:40.421 --> 00:01:41.463
So will you.

16
00:01:48.262 --> 00:01:51.056
You are good.
but you're going down.

17
00:01:51.223 --> 00:01:54.269
You forget.
I still have one more move.

18
00:02:05.238 --> 00:02:06.573
That's three.

19
00:02:07.115 --> 00:02:08.950
Where did you learn
to fight like that?

20
00:02:09.492 --> 00:02:11.286
If you want to be the best.

21
00:02:11.453 --> 00:02:14.706
you will have to seek
the true master.

22
00:03:34.453 --> 00:03:36.372
Robin. you are leaving us?

23
00:03:36.539 --> 00:03:37.581
I have to.

24
00:03:38.249 --> 00:03:41.085
Dude. you got your
butt kicked. It happens.

25
00:03:41.252 --> 00:03:44.088
Happens to some of us
more than others.

26
00:03:44.255 --> 00:03:46.799
Anyway. it doesn't mean
you have to quit.

27
00:03:46.924 --> 00:03:49.468
Yes. We will soon
locate this Kitaro

28
00:03:49.635 --> 00:03:52.054
and then it will be you
who is kicking the butt.

29
00:03:52.221 --> 00:03:55.057
I'm not quitting the team.
but my fight with Kitaro

30
00:03:55.182 --> 00:03:58.477
showed me how much I still have
to learn about martial arts.

31
00:03:58.602 --> 00:04:00.604
No problem.
I can help you train.

32
00:04:00.813 --> 00:04:03.440
I got a new computer-simulated
fight sequence in the gym.

33
00:04:03.566 --> 00:04:05.317
I've already trained
with the best.

34
00:04:05.442 --> 00:04:06.694
and apparently.
it wasn't enough.

35
00:04:07.278 --> 00:04:09.405
There's only one person
who can help me.

36
00:04:09.572 --> 00:04:11.824
You wish to learn
from this true master

37
00:04:11.991 --> 00:04:13.367
of whom the villain spoke?

38
00:04:13.868 --> 00:04:16.161
I'm not coming back
until I find him.

39
00:04:16.328 --> 00:04:18.080
What? Aw. come on. man.

40
00:04:18.247 --> 00:04:20.624
How do you know this true master
is even a good guy?

41
00:04:20.833 --> 00:04:22.001
How are you gonna find him?

42
00:04:22.126 --> 00:04:23.712
Do you even know
where you're going?

43
00:04:23.837 --> 00:04:26.298
- I'm not sure.
- Sounds like a plan.

44
00:04:27.007 --> 00:04:29.134
According to legend.
the true master lives

45
00:04:29.301 --> 00:04:31.177
in the mountains
on the other side of the world

46
00:04:31.344 --> 00:04:34.264
and can be found only by
the most serious of students.

47
00:04:34.431 --> 00:04:37.058
I'm in. When do we leave?
What should I pack?

48
00:04:37.183 --> 00:04:39.811
Will I need shots?
This is gonna be so cool.

49
00:04:40.395 --> 00:04:41.980
I have to go alone.

50
00:04:43.356 --> 00:04:46.067
That guy takes himself
way too seriously.

51
00:05:00.624 --> 00:05:01.875
Excuse me.

52
00:05:02.792 --> 00:05:03.793
Excuse me.

53
00:05:14.471 --> 00:05:15.263
Hello?

54
00:05:16.014 --> 00:05:17.390
Go away.

55
00:05:17.557 --> 00:05:19.059
Um. sorry to bother you.

56
00:05:19.225 --> 00:05:21.728
but I have come to train
with the true master.

57
00:05:23.605 --> 00:05:25.315
Of course you have.

58
00:05:25.482 --> 00:05:29.152
Boys like you always want
to train with the true master.

59
00:05:29.319 --> 00:05:32.197
Why else would you be here
in the middle of nowhere?

60
00:05:32.739 --> 00:05:34.324
So you know
where I can find him?

61
00:05:34.741 --> 00:05:36.493
He cannot train you.

62
00:05:37.118 --> 00:05:38.329
I've come a long way.

63
00:05:38.496 --> 00:05:42.249
If you don't mind. I'd like the true
master to tell me that himself.

64
00:05:42.458 --> 00:05:44.669
If you want to find
the true master.

65
00:05:44.835 --> 00:05:48.381
you must get to the top of
the mountain before night falls.

66
00:05:48.547 --> 00:05:49.507
Thanks.

67
00:05:50.299 --> 00:05:53.386
A route to the top
is very challenging.

68
00:05:53.511 --> 00:05:57.056
Many have tried.
Many have failed.

69
00:05:57.223 --> 00:05:58.849
I can handle it.

70
00:05:59.684 --> 00:06:02.436
You are not dressed properly
for such a journey.

71
00:06:02.603 --> 00:06:04.689
The true master
will only see you

72
00:06:04.855 --> 00:06:07.775
if you leave everything
from your world behind.

73
00:06:16.409 --> 00:06:17.827
The mask stays.

74
00:06:18.661 --> 00:06:19.996
Very well.

75
00:06:20.538 --> 00:06:21.455
My weapons!

76
00:06:21.789 --> 00:06:25.001
The true master
will not teach you with them.

77
00:06:31.866 --> 00:06:33.092
Can I go now?

78
00:06:33.259 --> 00:06:35.803
Come. I'll show you
where the path begins.

79
00:06:52.612 --> 00:06:54.239
No grappling hook.

80
00:06:54.406 --> 00:06:56.283
OK. I'll just swim across.

81
00:06:56.450 --> 00:06:58.452
Are you always so confident?

82
00:06:59.119 --> 00:07:01.580
Are you talking... to me?

83
00:07:02.164 --> 00:07:03.790
Do you see anyone else
on the bridge?

84
00:07:04.291 --> 00:07:06.001
I am the guardian of the river.

85
00:07:06.168 --> 00:07:07.878
If you wish to get
to the mountaintop.

86
00:07:08.378 --> 00:07:10.589
you must first get past me.

87
00:07:10.839 --> 00:07:12.049
OK.

88
00:07:15.469 --> 00:07:18.346
I don't really wish
to fight you. little warrior.

89
00:07:18.513 --> 00:07:22.768
Perhaps you have not noticed --
I am quite large.

90
00:07:23.268 --> 00:07:25.353
I've beaten guys
much bigger than you.

91
00:07:26.063 --> 00:07:27.064
Very well.

92
00:07:35.822 --> 00:07:38.283
Are you still
so certain you can win?

93
00:08:03.850 --> 00:08:05.560
Robin! You are--

94
00:08:07.814 --> 00:08:09.398
You are not Robin.

95
00:08:09.899 --> 00:08:11.776
Heh. uh. what's up?

96
00:08:11.943 --> 00:08:14.779
Beast Boy. why are you
wearing Robin's uniform?

97
00:08:15.404 --> 00:08:18.533
Call me Beast Boy Wonder.

98
00:08:19.325 --> 00:08:22.495
You should not be
in Robin's room when he is away.

99
00:08:22.662 --> 00:08:24.122
Come on. It's fun.

100
00:08:24.247 --> 00:08:25.998
Look at all the
cool stuff in here.

101
00:08:27.583 --> 00:08:29.502
Robin would say
that is not a toy.

102
00:08:29.752 --> 00:08:31.337
He would say
to leave that alone.

103
00:08:31.504 --> 00:08:33.131
If you're gonna talk like Robin.

104
00:08:33.798 --> 00:08:36.134
then maybe you should
dress like him. too.

105
00:08:36.300 --> 00:08:38.636
He has more than one uniform.

106
00:08:42.223 --> 00:08:43.808
Please. give up.

107
00:08:43.975 --> 00:08:45.476
You don't want to do this.

108
00:08:45.643 --> 00:08:47.395
There is still time
for you to turn back.

109
00:08:51.732 --> 00:08:53.359
I'll never turn back.

110
00:08:53.526 --> 00:08:55.570
I admire your commitment.

111
00:09:18.718 --> 00:09:21.345
You may proceed. but be warned --

112
00:09:21.512 --> 00:09:24.808
once you have crossed the river.
there is no turning back.

113
00:09:28.478 --> 00:09:30.939
Well. that was
a big waste of time.

114
00:09:41.033 --> 00:09:43.869
Next time an old woman tells you
to leave your shoes behind.

115
00:09:44.411 --> 00:09:45.662
take them anyway.

116
00:09:49.374 --> 00:09:51.168
How did you get past the bear?

117
00:09:51.335 --> 00:09:54.713
The same way you did -- I walked.

118
00:09:55.339 --> 00:09:57.716
Uh. excuse me.
but I'm kind of in a hurry.

119
00:09:58.425 --> 00:10:01.345
- You are very rude. you know?
- Huh?

120
00:10:01.970 --> 00:10:04.598
You're in such a hurry.
you do not have time

121
00:10:04.765 --> 00:10:08.101
to help an old woman
with a heavy burden?

122
00:10:09.019 --> 00:10:10.270
May I help you?

123
00:10:11.271 --> 00:10:12.714
Very well.

124
00:10:15.525 --> 00:10:18.111
How far until I reach
the true master?

125
00:10:18.695 --> 00:10:20.197
That all depends on you.

126
00:10:20.364 --> 00:10:22.908
You will see the true master
when you are ready.

127
00:10:23.075 --> 00:10:25.202
And how far do you want me
to carry these?

128
00:10:25.369 --> 00:10:28.872
Just far enough for an
old woman to rest her back.

129
00:10:28.956 --> 00:10:31.500
Now. since you are
in such a hurry.

130
00:10:31.667 --> 00:10:33.126
there is your path.

131
00:10:50.311 --> 00:10:53.022
What path? There's no way out.

132
00:10:53.189 --> 00:10:56.192
None that you can see.

133
00:10:57.510 --> 00:10:59.946
I am the guardian
of the cave.

134
00:11:00.446 --> 00:11:02.740
To continue your journey
to the top.

135
00:11:02.907 --> 00:11:06.077
you must first get past me.

136
00:11:07.245 --> 00:11:08.413
You're blind.

137
00:11:08.579 --> 00:11:11.165
I won't fight you.
It wouldn't be fair.

138
00:11:11.708 --> 00:11:14.877
Now the fight is even.

139
00:11:15.044 --> 00:11:17.839
Neither of us can see.

140
00:11:30.643 --> 00:11:33.187
It seems that
I have an advantage.

141
00:11:33.563 --> 00:11:36.524
I've defeated the bear.
and I will defeat you.

142
00:11:39.193 --> 00:11:41.738
Not if you cannot see me.

143
00:11:42.030 --> 00:11:44.615
You only see
what is right in front of you.

144
00:11:44.991 --> 00:11:49.370
If you want to find me.
you must go beyond what you see.

145
00:11:50.830 --> 00:11:53.709
You cannot trust your eyes.

146
00:11:58.797 --> 00:12:02.301
You cannot trust your ears.

147
00:12:03.744 --> 00:12:06.347
I could be anywhere.

148
00:12:11.602 --> 00:12:12.795
Gotcha.

149
00:12:16.357 --> 00:12:19.485
Very well. You may proceed.

150
00:12:31.914 --> 00:12:34.124
At this rate.
I'll never get anywhere.

151
00:12:42.549 --> 00:12:44.176
Titans. go!

152
00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:51.558
<i>Wah! Hyah! Gah gar!
Ooh! Gah gah!</i>

153
00:12:57.272 --> 00:13:01.610
Why. Starfire. your hair
looks especially shiny today.

154
00:13:01.777 --> 00:13:02.653
Thank you. Robin.

155
00:13:02.903 --> 00:13:05.239
I rinsed. lathered.
and repeated.

156
00:13:08.493 --> 00:13:10.245
I can't believe you two

157
00:13:10.412 --> 00:13:13.206
would just barge into
Robin's room when he's gone.

158
00:13:13.373 --> 00:13:16.709
dress up in his uniform.
and pretend to be Robin...

159
00:13:16.918 --> 00:13:18.503
- Uh..
- Well...

160
00:13:19.170 --> 00:13:20.964
without me!

161
00:13:21.865 --> 00:13:23.466
Dude. suit up.

162
00:13:23.675 --> 00:13:26.219
Oh. yes.
Come Robining with us.

163
00:13:26.386 --> 00:13:28.138
It is most delightful.

164
00:13:33.059 --> 00:13:34.269
You couldn't just take a class.

165
00:13:34.519 --> 00:13:36.312
You had to travel
around the world.

166
00:13:36.479 --> 00:13:38.565
There must be an easier way
up this mountain.

167
00:13:38.731 --> 00:13:42.444
There is an easy way
up this hill and a right way.

168
00:13:42.777 --> 00:13:44.028
Which do you choose?

169
00:13:44.696 --> 00:13:45.864
How did you get up there?

170
00:13:46.364 --> 00:13:48.533
Same as you -- I climbed.

171
00:13:50.493 --> 00:13:53.163
How much farther is it
until I reach the mountaintop?

172
00:13:53.329 --> 00:13:57.500
Such a journey cannot be measured
in steps taken. young warrior.

173
00:13:57.917 --> 00:14:01.713
Look. I just want to know if
we're talking feet. yards. or miles.

174
00:14:02.213 --> 00:14:04.048
If you keep stopping to chat.

175
00:14:04.215 --> 00:14:07.635
you will never make it
up the mountain before sunset.

176
00:14:08.787 --> 00:14:10.221
Thanks for your help.

177
00:14:12.432 --> 00:14:15.768
Bad guys. beware.
There's a new Robin in town.

178
00:14:21.734 --> 00:14:23.152
OK. man. My turn.

179
00:14:26.113 --> 00:14:27.740
<i>Robin calling Robin.</i>

180
00:14:28.157 --> 00:14:29.408
Robin here. Over.

181
00:14:29.575 --> 00:14:33.037
No. not you. Robin.
The other Robin.

182
00:14:33.871 --> 00:14:34.830
What's up. Robin?

183
00:14:37.666 --> 00:14:39.585
Well. this is just disturbing.

184
00:14:40.127 --> 00:14:43.130
Disturbing. yet magnificent.
Join us.

185
00:14:43.297 --> 00:14:45.966
I never knew wearing a cape
was so much fun.

186
00:14:46.133 --> 00:14:48.385
It is wonderful to be Robin.

187
00:14:48.552 --> 00:14:50.804
Yeah.
He has all the best stuff.

188
00:14:51.430 --> 00:14:53.349
Uh... right.

189
00:14:54.266 --> 00:14:57.937
Come on. Haven't you ever wondered
what it would be like to be Robin?

190
00:14:58.103 --> 00:15:00.189
You know you want to try it.

191
00:15:15.579 --> 00:15:18.040
I am the guardian of the trees.

192
00:15:18.858 --> 00:15:20.334
And if I want
to get up the mountain.

193
00:15:20.501 --> 00:15:22.086
I must first defeat you.

194
00:15:24.129 --> 00:15:26.090
How did you know
I was going to say that?

195
00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:28.717
Do you know what I am going
to say next?

196
00:15:28.884 --> 00:15:31.136
- No.
- Me neither.

197
00:15:31.720 --> 00:15:35.099
Been a while since anyone has
gotten this far up the mountain.

198
00:15:35.432 --> 00:15:39.938
You must be a good warrior to
have defeated the bear and the snake.

199
00:15:40.105 --> 00:15:42.107
Let's get this over with.

200
00:15:42.566 --> 00:15:43.692
No. no. no. no. no.

201
00:15:43.858 --> 00:15:46.736
We do not need to fight so soon.
Would you like some tea?

202
00:15:47.070 --> 00:15:49.823
I just want to fight you
so I can get to the top.

203
00:15:49.990 --> 00:15:51.408
Yes. I see.

204
00:15:51.575 --> 00:15:53.618
We are very serious.

205
00:15:53.952 --> 00:15:55.453
Youth. let's go.

206
00:16:04.796 --> 00:16:07.465
Monkey see. monkey do.

207
00:16:10.260 --> 00:16:11.970
Monkey just made a fool of you.

208
00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:15.724
Unless you could
quickly grow a tail.

209
00:16:15.890 --> 00:16:18.310
it appears
you are at a disadvantage.

210
00:16:41.958 --> 00:16:43.877
Monkey see. monkey do.

211
00:16:51.719 --> 00:16:53.054
Very well.

212
00:17:12.615 --> 00:17:13.866
Finally.

213
00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:27.004
Your journey to find
the true master ends now.

214
00:17:33.995 --> 00:17:36.347
Kitaro. why are you here?

215
00:17:36.639 --> 00:17:39.100
To train with the true master.
of course.

216
00:17:39.266 --> 00:17:41.310
You said you'd already
trained with him.

217
00:17:41.602 --> 00:17:43.187
That's what
I wanted you to think.

218
00:17:43.688 --> 00:17:45.231
I knew if I told you.

219
00:17:45.398 --> 00:17:47.483
you would go and seek
the true master.

220
00:17:47.650 --> 00:17:51.195
and all I had to do was
follow you up the mountain.

221
00:17:51.779 --> 00:17:52.863
Why did you need me?

222
00:17:53.364 --> 00:17:55.282
I could have come up
without you.

223
00:17:55.449 --> 00:17:58.994
but then I would be tired
from fighting all the challenges

224
00:17:59.161 --> 00:18:00.496
like you are.

225
00:18:00.705 --> 00:18:02.957
I'm not too tired
to finish what I started.

226
00:18:07.254 --> 00:18:09.381
You don't deserve to train
with the true master.

227
00:18:09.548 --> 00:18:11.216
You haven't earned it.

228
00:18:11.341 --> 00:18:14.928
I deserve it more than you.
I am the better fighter.

229
00:18:20.600 --> 00:18:22.686
You aren't so tough
without your weapons.

230
00:18:23.061 --> 00:18:25.147
I still have your weapons.

231
00:18:35.157 --> 00:18:36.700
Rise. young warrior.

232
00:18:36.867 --> 00:18:40.328
You must get up.
Your journey is not over.

233
00:18:41.121 --> 00:18:42.330
I can't fight him.

234
00:18:42.497 --> 00:18:44.958
He has all my weapons.
I have nothing.

235
00:18:45.125 --> 00:18:48.712
When you began your journey.
you were determined.

236
00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:52.591
Nothing could stop you.
and now that you are so close.

237
00:18:52.758 --> 00:18:55.886
are you willing
to give up so easily?

238
00:18:56.595 --> 00:18:58.597
It was easier at the beginning.

239
00:18:58.764 --> 00:19:00.807
Beginnings are often easier.

240
00:19:00.974 --> 00:19:04.060
but think of all that you have
accomplished along your journey.

241
00:19:04.186 --> 00:19:06.104
what you have learned
from your battles

242
00:19:06.188 --> 00:19:09.274
with the bear.
the snake. the monkey.

243
00:19:09.399 --> 00:19:11.526
What's the point of fighting
my way up the mountain

244
00:19:11.693 --> 00:19:14.029
when someone else is just going
to come up the easy way?

245
00:19:14.196 --> 00:19:17.783
There is always going to be
someone who does things the easy way.

246
00:19:17.866 --> 00:19:21.996
but that should not stop you
from doing things the right way.

247
00:19:22.163 --> 00:19:24.540
It is your journey.
young warrior.

248
00:19:24.582 --> 00:19:27.251
Only you decide when it ends.

249
00:19:32.882 --> 00:19:36.302
True master.
I am ready to train.

250
00:19:36.594 --> 00:19:39.013
You will see the true master
when you are ready.

251
00:19:43.042 --> 00:19:45.394
Give up.
You cannot defeat me.

252
00:19:45.603 --> 00:19:47.772
I've beaten guys
much bigger than you.

253
00:19:52.318 --> 00:19:54.654
Claws of the iron bear.

254
00:19:57.698 --> 00:20:01.035
How are you going to beat me
if you cannot even see me?

255
00:20:02.578 --> 00:20:04.413
I don't need to see you.

256
00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:09.585
Strike of the flying serpent.

257
00:20:15.758 --> 00:20:18.678
I see you are serious
about winning.

258
00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:21.264
So am I.

259
00:20:25.601 --> 00:20:27.436
Duel of the leaping monkey.

260
00:20:39.575 --> 00:20:40.492
Huh?

261
00:20:44.413 --> 00:20:47.332
There's an easy way
and a hard way down this hill.

262
00:20:47.499 --> 00:20:49.167
Looks like your taking
the hard way.

263
00:20:53.672 --> 00:20:55.674
The true master must train me!

264
00:20:58.677 --> 00:21:00.387
You did not
make it up the mountain

265
00:21:00.554 --> 00:21:02.014
on your own skills.

266
00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:05.350
You tried before on your own.
but could not make it.

267
00:21:05.517 --> 00:21:08.145
You are a thief and a cheater.

268
00:21:08.395 --> 00:21:10.397
The true master
will not train you --

269
00:21:10.564 --> 00:21:12.900
not now. not ever.

270
00:21:12.983 --> 00:21:15.903
- But...
- Take him off my mountain.

271
00:21:21.700 --> 00:21:24.494
Consider this a gift
for showing me the way.

272
00:21:26.496 --> 00:21:29.666
You're the true master.
but why didn't you tell me?

273
00:21:29.791 --> 00:21:31.752
You never asked.

274
00:21:31.919 --> 00:21:35.547
So why was it so important that
I get to the top before sunset?

275
00:21:35.756 --> 00:21:39.468
It is much easier to see
the path when it's not dark.

276
00:21:39.593 --> 00:21:43.722
All this time. I thought there was some
deep meaning to everything you were saying.

277
00:21:44.348 --> 00:21:46.350
Ahh. young warrior.

278
00:21:46.975 --> 00:21:49.728
you take things
much too seriously.

279
00:21:50.729 --> 00:21:53.441
I am ready to train with you.
true master.

280
00:21:53.608 --> 00:21:55.610
I believe you are.

281
00:22:03.660 --> 00:22:07.413
Do you desire another slice
of the cheese. Robin?

282
00:22:07.580 --> 00:22:10.291
Thanks. Robin.
Got room for another one. Robin?

283
00:22:10.458 --> 00:22:12.961
Don't mind if I do. Robin.

284
00:22:14.462 --> 00:22:17.006
You know. Robins.
I have to admit --

285
00:22:17.173 --> 00:22:19.175
the mask makes me feel cool.

286
00:22:23.972 --> 00:22:25.765
Huh. Pizza. Sweet!

287
00:22:28.518 --> 00:22:29.686
You know. Robins.

288
00:22:29.811 --> 00:22:32.313
the mask makes me
feel cool. too.

288
00:22:33.305 --> 00:23:33.346
